race.description: Kia Ora Bloodlines To Headlines Handicap
race.comment: BAND OF BROTHERS (5) gets a much better setup for this with the claim after doing all the work early from the wide gate when a tenacious third over 1400m at Eagle Farm. Strengthened over the break and no excuses from the inside barrier. STEP ASIDE (7) no Cool Jakey to contend with here, and better suited back to the 1300m. Will go back from the gate and launch late. JUST PARTY (6) costly commodity who gets his final chance back to his right trip from the low draw. RHYTHM OF LOVE (4) returns from a lengthy break. Talented on his day and placed in Group 3 grade last June. Should be forward enough for this with the two searching trials. Gets his chance with Rawiller aboard.
